snippet: Giannis Antetokounmpo finished with 28 points, 14 assists and 11 rebounds, and Milwaukee handed the Nets their fourth loss in a row.
abstract: NBA Roundup; Milwaukee Bucks defeat Brooklyn Nets, 109-100; other basketball scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Giannis Antetokounmpo finished with 28 points, 14 assists and 11 rebounds, and Milwaukee handed the Nets their fourth loss in a row.
